"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-04-05-french-diver-falls-off-board-slip-olympic-inauguration-dive-20595261\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tbrowser thatsupports HTML5 \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tvideo  Up Next  A French Olympic diver suffered an unfortunate mishap in front of PresidentEmmanuel Macronwhen he slipped and fell off a board during an exhibition event at the opening of the country's\\u00a0newOlympicAquatics Centre.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 43, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.1599133238191643e-13, \"text\": \"JavaScript\", \"types\": [\"Q9143\", \"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\"}, {\"begin\": 105, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"score\": 0.9999999998358362, \"rank\": 1.6409838342762054e-10, \"text\": \"HTML5\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\"}, {\"begin\": 137, \"end\": 143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9866099963338011, \"rank\": 0.01307524811887884, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexis Jandard was one of three divers selected to perform the synchronised plunge as part of an inauguration ceremony at the aquatics complex on the outskirts ofParis.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jandard's effort on the three-metre springboard, however, went horribly wrong when he slipped on the board after taking his first jump.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the other two divers took off to complete the dive, Jandard landed awkwardly on his back before falling headfirst into the water.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old, who finished 16th at the Tokyo Olympics in 2021, did not sustain any serious injuries from the fall but saw the funny side as he posted a picture on Instagram showcasing red scrapes down his back from the fall.\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 956, \"end\": 965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.505341466109823e-20, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Have fun, now's the time to take the mickey because I deserve it big time,' he said in a video on social media.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I want to reassure everyone.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not hurt myself.\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a bit of blood, but it's not serious.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not going to stop me training this afternoon.'\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to French outletRMC Sport,the diver added: 'I have broken boards before, but the board had never broken me before.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1299, \"end\": 1305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9866099963338011, \"rank\": 0.01307524811887884, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now it has.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1422, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I would have preferred this ceremony to have gone well from start to finish.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was that little hitch.\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If it made people smile a little, so much the better.\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We know our sport.\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We know what it entails.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We know that these things can happen.\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1668, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no such thing as zero risk.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It had to happen in front of the President and the whole of France.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5020729743150089, \"rank\": 0.49351770869393147, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we chose the right moment.'\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Team GB flag fury is just the latest Olympic kit controversy  ArrowMORE:Olympic legend 'disgusted' at change to Team GB Union Jack  ArrowMORE:Every word Andy Murray has said about his upcoming retirement from tennis  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 2272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2057, \"end\": 2064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\